ot matter whatsoever, what the people around you think you can or cannot do. What really matters is what you think about your capabilities.\n\n- Abhijit Naskar, The Film Testament\n|\nIf I am looking for inspiration, then I read the religious scriptures.\n\n- Steven\n|\nUntil you discover what you can do with your time, you won’t know how to go about crucial things\n\n- Sunday"